---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---

<section class="hero">
  <p class="hero__label">UX Design &amp; Product Strategy</p>
  <h1 class="hero__headline">Making<br>complexity<br><em>navigable.</em></h1>
  <div class="hero__footer">
    <p class="hero__body">I work at the intersection of user research, system design, and business strategy — turning ambiguous problems into decisions that hold.</p>
    <span class="hero__scroll">Scroll to explore</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="selected">
  <div class="selected__header">
    <span class="selected__title">Selected work</span>
    <a href="/work/" class="selected__link">All projects →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="work-grid">
  {%- for post in collections.caseStudies | reverse -%}
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="work-card{% if loop.first %} work-card--featured{% endif %}">
      <div class="work-card__image{% if not post.data.cover_image %} work-card__image--empty{% endif %}">
        {% if post.data.cover_image %}<img src="{{ post.data.cover_image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">{% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="work-card__body">
        <span class="work-card__num">0{{ loop.index }}</span>
        <div class="work-card__meta">
          <span class="tag">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
          {% if post.data.year %}<span class="tag">{{ post.data.year }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <h2 class="work-card__title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="work-card__summary">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
        <span class="work-card__link">View case study →</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="approach">
  <p class="approach__label">How I work</p>
  <div class="approach__items">
    <div class="approach__item">
      <span class="approach__num">01</span>
      <h3>Research before solutions</h3>
      <p>I run structured research to surface what's actually happening — not what stakeholders assume. The problem definition is half the work.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="approach__item">
      <span class="approach__num">02</span>
      <h3>Strategy informs design</h3>
      <p>I bring a business lens to every UX decision. A feature that users love but the business can't sustain isn't a solution — it's a delay.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="approach__item">
      <span class="approach__num">03</span>
      <h3>Iteration over perfection</h3>
      <p>I prototype early, test fast, and hold concepts loosely. The goal is learning — not being right the first time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
